data.description: Beautifully renovated home on 1.2 total acres in the North end of Dover. This 4 bed- 4 bath home has so much to offer. Beautiful Laminate flooring, plush carpet, full finished lower level. The Kitchen with dining area has ample cabinetry and includes the appliances. The sunken Livingroom includes a stone fireplace and French doors that lead to the paver patio. The laundry room has a 1/2 bath and also includes appliances, 2 nice size bedrooms and a full bath with marble flooring complete the main floor. The second level occupies the owners suite. The full bath offers marble flooring and shower, double lavatories and a large walk-in closet. There are sliding doors that lead out to a deck to relax and enjoy a good book. The full, finished lower level has two additional room for entertaining, the 4th bedroom and another bath with a beautiful walk-in tile shower, laminate floor and nice cabinetry. The furnace room has built in cabinets and plenty of storage and also includes a "dog washing" station. The 2 car attached garage has electric and is also heated. The home also include gutter guards. Close to shopping, highway access, eateries, etc. Schedule your private showing soon. This home will offer immediate possession after closing.
